title: Portal hacia Helen
description: Craig hace una conexión a larga distancia con un niño que ama el Arroyo tanto como él.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Diet
description: Gumball and Darwin discover the reason Dad's diet wasn't working was that he was actually on ten diets and eating a meal for each of them. They eventually manage to help him lose weight, but Richard's newfound buffness also brings out his more obnoxious side.

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Rock On
description: The Looney Builders are hired by Mac and Tosh Gopher to build them a home underground. Daffy can't remove rocks from the area fast enough and fails to ask for help.

title: Fashion Forward
description: When the Fashionistas launch a new line of brainwashing clothing, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop the fashion trend before it's too late.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: Sister Sitter
description: When Blossom and Bubbles get sick, Buttercup volunteers to take care of them for the day.

title: Charm School
description: At Gwen's college, Ben suspects a new teacher and new student are old enemies.

title: The Real Number One
description: When Thomas' #1 is covered by paint, he sets out to prove to himself that he is still number one, but when everything starts to go wrong for him, he learns what it really means to be #1.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: Cheerleading
description: Brock drags Master Frown along to join him in following his dream, to become the Flyer on a cheerleading team. They team up with Unikitty & the gang and go head to head against Really Old Edith and her rival cheer team of meanies. But when the gang finds Brock is too heavy to be the Flyer they're forced to try a bunch of ridiculous ways to get him off the ground.

title: Picture This!
description: The babies create their own endings to fairytales.

title: A Clean Sweep
description: Daffy tries to avoid cleaning up by sweeping his toys under a rug.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever/Just Desserts
description: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever: It's raining in Townsville and there is no crime or villainy afoot. So the girls must stay inside and come up with their very own Powerpuff adventure./Just Desserts: The Smith Family is back and they want revenge. Harold, Maryanne and the kids become a super villain team and make it their goal to destroy the perfect Powerpuff family.

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Gold Watch
description: Benson has to get to work on time so he can win a gold watch.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Sneakerheads
description: Apple & Onion need a Last Will and Testament if they are to protect their belongings from the state.

title: Crane
description: It's the first day on the job for Kareem the Crane, and he's feeling very nervous. Luckily, Blippi and FETCH are there to lend a helping hand! Working together they help Kareem to do his work. Kareem gains confidence and Blippi learns how cranes help to build a skyscraper!

title: Fight at the Museum
description: Alien artifacts in Bellwood attract enemies from the future and friends from the past.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: The Galactic Enforcers
description: Ben joins a trio of intergalactic alien heroes tracking down the bounty hunter Six Six. But this bunch of heroes is not all it's cracked up to be.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Ace of Squares
description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Patients
description: Clarence must somehow navigate the mind-numbing boredom of a doctor's office waiting room to earn the ultimate prize - candy from the reception desk candy jar.

title: Crowbar Jones
description: Pardo proyecta una película amateur épica que acaba de rodar para un grupo focal. Pero cuando se da cuenta de que la gente se marcha, debe descubrir formas de mantener interesada a la audiencia.

title: Speed Demon/Mojo Jonesin'
description: Mojo Jonesin':  When the children of Pokey Oaks become envious of the girls' superpowers, a mysterious figure offers them Chemical X. Now, the girls must fight their own classmates who have powers equal to their own./Speed Demon: The girls accidentally fly at the speed of light and when they arrive home, everything has changed. Fifty years have passed and the world has been taken over by Him.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Neighborhood Grill
description: Clarence is so troubled by the sight of his teacher in a social setting outside of school, he can't stop himself from intruding on her doomed blind date.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Joking Victim
description: When Lars pawns off all his work on Sadie, Steven helps out by working a shift at the Big Donut.

title: Mentiras lastimosas
description: Beth y Leshawna tratan de superarse uno a la otra con heridas falsas mientras compiten por la atención y comprensión de los otros niños en la guardería.

title: Dance Lessons
description: Panda volunteers to be Lucy's partner for a dance contest. But Panda doesn't have the heart to tell Lucy that she's a terrible dancer.

title: Los Porristas
description: Brock convence a Master Frown de acompañarlo para hacer realidad su sueño de convertirse en el volador de un equipo de animadoras. Se asocian con Unikitty y la banda y se enfrentan cara a cara con Edith y el equipo de porristas malvados que tienen como rivales. Pero cuando la banda descubre que Brock es demasiado pesado para ser el volador, se ven obligados a intentar un montón de formas ridículas de levantarlo del suelo.

title: Campeon del Cuadro
description: iCraig promete hacer que el juego de Cuatro Cuadros vuelva a ser divertido cuando desafía a su jugador más experto!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: Charm School's Out
description: During a family cookout at a forest campsite, Charmcaster users her magic to switch places with Gwen, but when Ben catches "Charmcaster" sneaking about, he attacks, unaware it's actually his cursed cousin!

title: Beastie Team Battle/Ajit and Lia
description: Beastie Team Battle: China Riot is on the lookout for a partner to team up with in the new Bakugan battle team tournament being held in Los Volmos. Riot may have only been after a brawling partner, but ends up with a new friend./Ajit and Lia: Lia knows the story of where Ajit found his Golden Baku-balls, but no one knows "how" he's able to partner with Golden Bakugan. To get the inside scoop, Lia tags along with Ajit at his new job as a security guard at the local Museum.

title: Champion of the Universe, Dan!/Operation Babysitter
description: Champion of the Universe, Dan!: Dan starts "sleep brawling", rolling out Drago causing damage and confusion while he's fast asleep. With the help of a "sleep expert", Ajit attempts to stop Dan and put his "sleep brawling" to rest once and for all./Operation Babysitter: Ajit lands a job babysitting a rambunctious toddler - Aiden. Having no experience with kids, Ajit recruits Wynton to help him out. Things get a little out of hand when Aiden rolls out - Krakelious. Now, Ajit and Wynton have a tiny Baku-brawler on their hands, with no way to stop him!

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: The Cast
description: After breaking his leg, Robin is confined to his room and spies through a telescope.

title: Buzz In
description: Bizzy Buzzard's mom hires The Looney Builders to build her family a new nest. Bizzy wants to help but keeps getting in the way creating all sorts of problems for the crew.

title: Wristy Business
description: Beth and Leshawna try to one-up each other with fake injuries as they compete for the attention and sympathy of the other kids at daycare.

title: Stay Goth, Poodle Girl, Stay Goth
description: Gwen accidentally brings a pink stuffed pony she loves to daycare and spends the day denying it's hers.

title: Daffy Did It!
description: Tweety blames Daffy for his mistake, and then has trouble living with the guilt of lying.

title: Pilot Expansion
description: Clarence, Sumo, and Jeff reminisce about the day they first met - although a few of the details are foggy.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: The Bakugan Battle League Dash/The Final Stage
description: The Bakugan Battle League Dash: With Dan and Ajit eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition, the remaining Awesome Brawlers - Shun, Wynton, Lia and Lightning race to complete the second stage of the competition. In order to make it to the final stage, the gang will have to pull together to defeat some tough competition./The Final Stage: It's the final stage of the Bakugan Battle League Tokyo Edition! The remaining Awesome Brawlers are ready to go, but just as the final round begins, the competitors are surprised with some unwelcome guests.

title: Always Be Crimefighting
description: Looking to motivate them, Robin tells the Titans to solve some crimes or they're fired.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Doorway to Helen
description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: The Cycle
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais discover that Mr Wilson has been picking on their Dad for most of his life; ever since he humiliated Richard with a high school prank. The kids try to work Dad through it but when their efforts fail, they realize that getting back at Mr Wilson is the only way to break the cycle.

title: Bad Little Boy
description: The princesses are sick and tired of Ice King's crazy Fionna & Cake stories, so Marceline stops by the Ice Kingdom to show him how it's done.

title: Clyde Five
description: Ben's country cousin wants to be a hero, too.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Lighthouse
description: The Bears find a lighthouse powered by a luminous creature.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: Twisted Sister/Cover Up
description: Twisted Sister: The girls decide they need some help fighting crime so they create another Powerpuff Girl. But they don't get the combination of sugar, spice and everything nice quite right./Cover Up: Blossom and Bubbles learn that Buttercup has secretly been rubbing a security blanket before every battle to make herself a super fighter. Can the girls convince Buttercup that her strength is within?

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Five More Short Graybles
description: Finn and Jake stick their thumbs in everything. Marceline tries to find her way to Wizard Bill's Music Shop. Ice King gets a new bride.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Ragtag
description: When the kingdom runs out of inspiration, Unikitty takes it on herself to re-inspire the citizens with a riveting game of kickball where she and the gang form a ragtag team of underdogs, who are supposed to win a miraculous unexpected victory against Master Frown, Brock & The Doom Lords. But when the Doom Lords end up stinking at kickball, and the people are uninspired by the good guys' easy victory, Unikitty switches things up and joins the real ragtag team, The Doom Lords, to help lead them to a victory that finally inspires the kingdom.

title: Jake the Dad
description: Jake's a daddy, but being a father and keeping his rainicorn pups from killing themselves or each other is a lot harder than he imagined.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: Easter Annihilation
description: When Cyborg's egg hunt tech stops working, the Titans go to their satellite to find out what happened.

title: Up a Tree
description: Finn and Jake are playing catch when Finn accidentally tosses their throwing disc into a gigantic tree.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Painting the Barn Song
description: The Boogie Barn needs a new coat of paint. The children and animals all want to help. Mei brings them the paint and they all have fun adding paint and mixing paint to create a multi-coloured Boogie Barn!

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: An Indirect Kiss
description: When Amethyst cracks her gemstone, Steven and the Crystal Gems go on a mission to heal her.

title: Rain Rain Go Away
description: Ella meets Frogalina (a frog ballerina) who shows her how to enjoy the rain with some splashy ballet dance moves. Inspired, Ella shows Go-Go the cat and Pablo the pig that rain is important, and fun, on Lellobee Farm.

title: Hair Cut-Ups
description: Lola is afraid of getting her first haircut.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Bats
description: Can you see in the dark? Blippi can't either! But on this adventure Blippi and FETCH fly around in the dark with Matt the Bat who shows them how he uses echolocation to see and hear in the dark! Who needs eyes when you can use echo-echo-echoes?

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Diggin' A Hole
description: Uncle Grandpa digs a hole.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Grades
description: Miss Simian discovers a failed test from Gumball's past that brings down his grade point average. This means he has to retake kindergarten all over again, much to her delight. But by demoting him Miss Simian has inadvertently brought herself down, and they're left with no choice but to team up if they want things back to normal.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Kyle
description: Nom Nom se reúne con Kyle, su hermano del que estaba distanciado.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: All the Little People
description: Magic Man secretly slips Finn a bag filled with miniature versions of Finn and all his friends.

title: Cyber Slammers
description: At Biggie Box Japan, Ben waits in an epic line for the release of the latest Sumo Slammers video game, Cyber Slammers, but Ben must save the store not from game-hungry customers, but from Steam Smythe, who wants to retro-fit a massive mech with steam punk powers!

title: Ducks
description: Blippi gets up close and personal with Declan the Duck in his quest to find how ducks float! Under the water, above the water, through feather tunnels and tooting air bubbles, Blippi and Declan work together to discover the answer.

title: Truffle Season
description: It's Truffle Season, Apple and Onion are Truffle Hunters and they will stop at nothing to taste a truffle.

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: La Grange Muralla
description: Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max hacen un viaje a la Gran Muralla, pero su aventura por poco termina arruinada por los temerarios LaGrange y Vin Etanol, que intentan saltar sobre el monumento internacional. Ben debe subirse al Rustbuggy para ahuyentar a los enemigos.

title: Beach Heads
description: After traveling to Tampa Beach, Florida, Team Tennyson hopes to get some much-needed rest & relaxation, but the tempests without a temper, the Weatherheads, have other plans that Ben must thwart: to build a new beach base!

title: Monster Buddies
description: Steven accidentally releases a monster from a gem bubble and attempts to tame its wild, violent instincts.

title: Campeones por accidente
description: Cuando el reino se queda sin inspiración, Unikitty se encarga de volver a inspirar a los ciudadanos con un fascinante juego de kickball en el que ella y la banda forman un equipo de débiles, que se supone que obtendrán una victoria milagrosa e inesperada contra Master Frown, Brock y los Señores de la Muerte. Pero cuando los Señores de la Muerte pierden el partido de kickball, y la gente no se siente inspirada por la victoria fácil de los chicos buenos, Unikitty cambia las cosas y se une al desamparado equipo enemigo para ayudarlos a conseguir una victoria que finalmente inspire al reino.

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: Tough Luck
description: Gwen's Lucky Girl powers return when she buys a magical stone at a magic convention in Las Vegas. However, Hex is after the same stone, and after his niece breaks him out of prison, the two set off to retrieve the stone.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: The Tiger Train
description: When Yong Bao visits Sodor, a jealous Thomas sets out to prove he's the braver train and challenges Yong Bao to a series of bravery challenges, only to have his plan backfire.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Rook Tales
description: Rook's former teacher will preserve Revonnahgander traditions at any cost.

title: Noches heladas dos
description: Polar sale a una aventura nocturna para rescatar a Yana, su amiga, de unos enemigos familiares.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: En la Oscuridad
description: La princesa Vania revela una entrada secreta que conduce a una mina subterránea bajo Shintaro donde se guardan los oscuros secretos de la ciudad.

title: Superhero Feud
description: Control Freak pits the Titans against the DC Superhero Girls to determine who is the best team in the universe.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: The Ballad of Mr. Baumann
description: The grouchy storekeeper has a big secret, and she's not of this Earth.

title: Juego Terminado
description: Unagami entra al mundo real y aterroriza a la ciudad de Ninjago mientras Jay, Zane y Pixal intentan evitar el desastre reuniendo a Unagami con Dyer.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Birds Nest
description: A storm has destroyed Jodie the Blue Jays bird nest! Good thing Blippi and FETCH are there to help. While FETCH is on egg-sitting duty, Jodie and Blippi go on a heist mission to acquire the materials needed to rebuild. It's never an impossible mission when friends work together!

title: O'Little Tree
description: Mei shows Ella and Rishi the magic of Christmas - by growing an adorable Christmas tree in the middle of the farm.

title: Roller Coasting
description: Thomas wants to show Percy what it's like to ride a roller coaster, so Thomas turns the tracks of Sodor into a thrill ride.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Falafel's Car Keys
description: Apple & Onion are deemed responsible enough to borrow Falafel's car for their first road trip together. Nothing will go wrong, and they're going to make sure of that… by getting some practice in.

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Broken Boogie
description: When the Boogie Man loses his mojo, Uncle Grandpa steps in to help.

title: The Climb
description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

title: No Power, No Problem!
description: When the power goes out all over Sodor, Thomas and Friends must use brain-power to navigate the island in creative new ways.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Invasion of the Booger Snatchers
description: Harold believes that the picture day photographer is somehow turning the kids into well behaved zombies.

title: Guidance
description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

title: El Templo de la Locura
description: Jay debe enfrentarse solo a Unagami en el juego final, pero Unagami tiene una batalla más grande al enfrentarse a la verdad sobre su propia identidad.

title: Goma pegajosa
description: A Beth se le atasca la goma de mascar en el cabello de Leshawna y tiene que sacarla- sin que Leshawna descubra que está ahí.

title: Invasion de los mocos ladrones
description: Harold cree que el fotógrafo del día de la foto oficial está convirtiendo a los niños en zombies que se portan bien.

title: Gum and Gummer
description: Beth gets her gum stuck in Leshawna's hair and has to get it out - without Leshawna finding out it's there.

title: Safety First
description: Concerned about Puppycorn's propensity to hurt himself constantly, the gang places him into Richard's old Safety Suit. The suit does indeed keep him safe, but when Puppycorn purposefully puts himself in danger the suit goes into lock down, and won't allow him to move. Now the gang must figure out a way to get him out of the Safety Suit.

title: Red, White and Bruised/Beaky Buzzard Gags: Bunny/Jet Porkpelled
description: Tweety Bird builds a nest in a military base to keep safe from Sylvester. Beaky Buzzard goes hunting. Porky tries Daffy Duck's new jet pack.

title: Uncle Grandpa's Uncle Grandpa
description: Uncle Grandpa is in trouble! If only he could call an Uncle Grandpa for help.

title: Paint Job
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to paint a house.

title: Take the Cake
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to deliver a cake to Maellard's birthday party.

title: Kyle
description: Nom Nom is reunited with his long lost brother, Kyle.

title: Temple Bears
description: The Bears search for a house key in a puzzle-filled temple.

title: Icy Nights II
description: Ice Bear goes on a late-night adventure to rescue his friend, Yana, from some familiar foes.

title: Too Gross for Comfort
description: Clarence's innocent attempt to ingratiate Chelsea, a girl, into a boys only tree fort puts Sumo in charge of an effort to gross Chelsea out and preserve the status quo.

title: Primer Vuelo
description: Cuando la banda hace un viaje en avión, Halcondrilo está al mando ya que hoy da el examen para obtener su licencia de capitán. Como a Richard le da terror volar, Unikitty y Perricornio pasan el caótico vuelo tratando de ayudarlo a vencer su miedo, mientras la Dra. Fox acompaña a Halcondrilo en la cabina para ayudarlo a aprobar su examen.

title: LaGrange Muraille
description: While visiting China, Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max take a trek to the Great Wall, but their adventure is nearly ruined by daredevils LaGrange and Vin Ethanol trying to jump the international monument, and Ben must hop into the Rustbuggy to chase away the fast and furious foes.

title: Cave Sweet Cave
description: After the Joker floods the Batcave, the Batwheels evacuate and relocate to a nearby parking garage. As they adapt to their temporary home, they learn important lessons about family and making the most of what you have.

title: Don Pellizco
description: JP lleva a sus amigos de viaje para encontrar el cangrejo de río más grande del Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Catching the Wave
description: Pops wants to catch a wave.

title: El Peor Rescate de la Historia
description: Los Ninjas intentan rescatar a Cole, pero las discusiones entre prisioneros alertan al Hechicero Calavera, y hace prisioneros a los otros Ninjas.

title: Derretidor
description: Cuando Chef le dice a Beth que no comprará el nuevo juguete súper increíble que ella quiere porque ya tienen mucho con qué jugar, ella emprende una misión para librarse de sus juguetes.

title: Melter Skelter
description: When Chef tells Beth he won't buy the new super amazing toy she wants because they already have plenty to play with, she goes on a mission to get rid of their toys.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Cyber Luchadores
description: En Biggie Box Japón, Ben espera en una fila épica el lanzamiento de Cyber Luchadores, el último videojuego de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero muy pronto, Ben debe salvar la tienda: no de los clientes ansiosos por comprar el juego sino de Vapor Smythe, ique quiere modernizar un mecanismo gigantesco con sus vandálicos poderes de vapor!

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: A escalar
description: iEl teléfono de Craig se atasca en el Monte Sicomoro, el árbol más alto del Arroyo!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Crowbar Jones
description: Grizz screens an epic amateur movie he just made for a focus group. But when he notices people are leaving he must figure out ways to keep the audience engaged.

title: The Ex
description: Gumball discovers that Rob, his old nemesis, is "neme-seeing" someone else now. Devastated that Rob has fallen out of hate with him, Gumball refuses to accept that his ex-nemesis has moved on and does his best to sabotage Rob's blossoming relationship with his new foe, Banana Joe.

title: Mo Job/Pet Feud
description: Mo Job: Princess hires Mojo to devise the perfect plan to destroy the girls, who are quite shocked when they find Princess has powers equal to their own./Pet Feud: The Professor creates the perfect little pet. But there's only one catch: he can only be fed once a day. When the girls each feed him, they find that their sweet little friend has become a wild beast!

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: The Need for Feed/The Zipline Sisters of Treetop Woods
description: MacBarm is bringing food to his hungry chickens, that is, until all of the food falls out of his truck./Grandma and her twin sister want to recreate their old zipline act, but quickly discover that the zipline no longer exists!

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: They Lurk Below
description: Max's old friend has built the world's only underwater resort, and Ben, Gwen and Max are invited for a sneak peak. But it turns out in order to power the resort, Max's friend took an energy orb from a race of underwater aliens. Now, the aliens want their energy orb back and destroy the resort in order to get it.

title: Once More into the Maze/Grandpas in the Wild
description: Once More into the Maze: Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett were spotted at the ruins where the great core cell is housed! Alarmed by the report from Benton Dusk, the Awesome Brawlers head to the Yucatan Peninsula to investigate./Grandpas in the Wild: During an all-out brawl with Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett, the Awesome Brawlers are hit with an attack that sends everyone spiraling to various parts of the maze. Split up from the rest of the gang, Wynton and Lightning find themselves in a strange unfamiliar part of the maze. While trying to get their bearings, they discover some new golden allies.

title: Citizen Tabes
description: After accidentally wounding an animal, Ranger Tabes quits her job. The Bears do what they can to coax her out of retirement.

title: Shintaro
description: Los Ninjas están invitados a asistir a la fiesta de cumpleaños de la princesa Vania en la ciudad de Shintaro. Llevan al Maestro Wu que está deprimido.

title: Lowlifes
description: Apple & Onion cannot allow themselves to be viewed by society- and more importantly by smug old Chicken Nugget-as lowlifes.

title: The Temple of Madness
description: Jay must stand alone against Unagami in the end-game, yet Unagami has a bigger battle in facing the truth about his own identity.

title: La ciudadana Tabes
description: Luego de lastimar por accidente a un animal, la guardabosques Tabes renuncia a su trabajo. Los Osos hacen todo lo posible para persuadirla de jubilarse.

title: Cheep Thrills
description: After finding a baby monster in the park, Bubbles insists on adopting it without considering the consequences!

title: Scaredy-Bat
description: When Batman refuses to engage Joker in a race, Prank goads Bam into a rematch. Can Bam learn to not give in to the bully's dares and take the high road?

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: Steven and the Stevens
description: Steven needs a musical partner for an upcoming show, and uses a time travel device to recruit the perfect bandmate, HIMSELF!

title: The Last Kid in the Creek
description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: Odd Bubbles Out
description: When Donny the Unicorn visits, Bubbles becomes jealous of his new friend.

title: Ultimate Weapon
description: When Max finds out that part of an alien weapon has been unearthed in Texas, he becomes obsessed with finding it. In doing so, he leads Ben and Gwen on a wild adventure.

title: Princesa gotica
description: Gwen lleva por accidente un pony de peluche rosado que le encanta a la guardería, y pasa todo el día negando que es suyo.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Anger Management
description: Aunt Grandma's back is causing more trouble for Uncle Grandpa.

title: Into the Dark
description: When Cole investigates a mysterious visitor, the ninja aren't sure what to believe. Cole is frustrated with this lack of team support, until Princess Vania reveals a secret entrance that leads to an underground mine beneath Shintaro - where the city's dark secrets are held.

title: Volcan
description: Un volcán súper gruñón aparece en el reino. Por eso, Unikitty lleva a la banda a una misión épica para alegrarlo con una de las flores de FeeBee antes de que entre en erupción y destruya el reino. Pero FeeBee no tiene ganas de compartir sus queridas flores, y trata de sabotear la misión. ¿Será capaz Unikitty de convencerla de los beneficios de compartir para salvar el reino de la destrucción?

title: Game Over
description: Unagami breaks into the real world and terrorizes Ninjago City while Jay, Zane and Pixal attempt to prevent disaster by reuniting Unagami with his creator, Milton Dyer.

title: Expert or Liar
description: Rigby wants to redeem himself by winning on "Expert or Liar."

title: Back to Our Regular Time Period
description: The Bears find themselves trapped in the wrong time period.

title: Mr. McStuffles
description: Daffy doesn't want to give up his old toy, even after he's outgrown it.

title: Happy Bouncy Fun Town
description: The Bears land in the cheeriest place of all time, but Ice Bear starts to feel out of place.

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: Shintaro
description: The ninja are invited to attend the birthday party of Princess Vania, in the distant Kingdom of Shintaro. They depart, bringing along Master Wu, unaware that he is feeling his age…

title: Mirror Gem
description: Steven befriends a magical mirror that can mysteriously communicate with him.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Pizza Steve's Past
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang learn of Pizza Steve's past stint in the food service industry. Pizza Steve wasn't always the Pizza Steve they know and love.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Belson's Sleepover
description: Belson invites Clarence and friends to a sleepover party, with a catch: whoever can survive the night's pranks and scares will win Belson's old Acedia game system!

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Old Macdonald
description: Rishi goes around the farm with Ella, organising all the animals so they can have a soccer game!

title: First Flight
description: The gang is taking an airplane trip together, and Hawk is at the helm since today he's taking his captain's license test. However Richard is terrified of flying, so Unikitty & Puppycorn spend the chaotic flight trying to help Rick conquer his fear of flying while Dr Fox joins Hawk in the cockpit to help him pass his test. After a destructive and dangerous flight, Rick makes it safetly back on the ground (after surviving the plane crashing). Hawk fails his test but gets to take it again next week, so the gang is excited for another free flight.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Camp Fear
description: When a race of alien mushrooms takes over a summer camp, Ben discovers a whole new alien to battle the menace.

title: The Stars
description: When Dad gives Larry's hairdresser a bad review for saying he's bald, he gets offered a free haircut. This inspires Gumball and Darwin to go on a reviewing spree across town, forcing Larry to give them stuff with the threat of a bad review. Just because the customer is always right doesn't mean that what they're doing isn't wrong.

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: The Tokyo Catastrophe/Bakugan Battle League Finale
description: The Tokyo Catastrophe: Haavik has highjacked the Bakugan Battle league - Tokyo Edition! He's been using the tournament as a platform for his sinister plot to bring chaos and destruction to the city of Tokyo./Bakugan Battle League Finale: Haavik unleashes an army of unruly Bakugan to bring his own brand of chaos and destruction to the city of Tokyo. It's all hands-on-deck to stop the invasion, and foil Haavik's plot.

title: Can-Do Submarine Crew
description: Thomas and Percy think they're great communicators, but when they're tasked with delivering a submarine to Vicarstown, communication becomes a bit more difficult… to say the least!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Big Pinchy
description: JP leads his friends on a voyage to find the biggest crayfish in the creek.

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: La seguridad es primero
description: Preocupados por la propensión de Perricornio a lastimarse constantemente, la banda le coloca el viejo traje de seguridad de Richard. El traje lo mantiene a salvo, pero cuando Perricornio se pone en peligro a propósito, el traje se bloquea y le impide moverse. Ahora la banda debe encontrar la manera de sacarlo del traje de seguridad.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Filthy Rich
description: What does it take to be truly content? Whatever it takes, Apple and Onion are going to achieve it.

title: Shake the Apple Tree
description: It's the end of the summer and the trees are full of delicious apples ready to be picked!

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: Presidential Punchout
description: When Morbucks enters the Student Body President race, Blossom sinks to her level to secure the win.

title: Volcano
description: A super-grumpy volcano appears in the kingdom, so Unikitty takes the gang on an epic quest to cheer it up with one of FeeBee's flowers before it erupts and destroys the kingdom.

title: Big Ben 10
description: Cuando Ben y su familia viajan a Londres para visitar el legendario Big Ben, los hermanos Bicho están allí para darles la bienvenida, obviamente con un nuevo plan escandalosamente exagerado: iencoger la campana del Big Ben para robarla!

title: I Am Chair
description: During a stressful trip to the mall, Robin finds peace in a massage chair.

title: Waffle Cones for Whiffles
description: The Whiffles are too hot and tired to work because their daily treat, colorful ice in Waffles Cones delivered by the whimsical "Icelings," hasn't arrived - the Icelings have mysteriously disappeared. As the Care Bears search for them, Share volunteers to make the treats. It's much more than she can handle but she's determined to go-it-alone and not ask for help. Things get out of hand and Share ends up snared in Bluster's trap with the Icelings, who help her to realize that we get more done when we work together.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Lecciones de Baile
description: Panda se ofrece como voluntario para ser el compañero de Lucy en un concurso de baile. Pero no se atreve a decirle a Lucy que es una pésima bailarina.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: The Worst Rescue Ever
description: The ninja attempt to rescue Cole, but the bickering of his fellow prisoners, the Geckles and Munce, alerts the Skull Sorcerer, and soon the ninja are prisoners too.

title: That's the Way the Windmill Blows!/Mecha Machine Makers!
description: The windmill isn't turning, which means Sunny Field Farm has no power. The windmill needs to turn again so Zee can launch his rocket!/Izzy and Timmy are making a bird caller for Grandma, but have trouble connecting pieces of their machine.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 3
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Flies
description: Lunch is ready! Prepared to eat his delicious sandwich, Blippi notices his old friend Horace the Fly. Horace is walking upside down on the ceiling, and after shrinking down, Blippi joins him. But how does Horace stick to the ceiling? A musical song and dance from Horace is the best way to find out!

title: Big Ben 10
description: When Ben and family go to London to visit the legendary Big Ben, the Bugg Brothers are there to greet them, with yet another outrageously over the top plan of course: to shrink the Big Ben bell in order to steal it!

title: Bath on the Nile
description: The Bears find themselves in an ancient Egyptian spa, but Grizz refuses to take a bath.
